name: Parvati Valley
description: A view from Kheerganga Trek, hilltop at 4:30 am, Kheerganga trek is one of the most recommended trek situated in Parvati Valley in the state of Himachal Pradesh, India and is known for the most astonishing views. After a 9km long steep uphill trek, this view was like finding an oasis in the middle of a desert.
